# Fact Check — AI Adoption & Workforce Impact in Spain (2024–2025)

**Methodology:** V/I/H Epistemic Tagging System

- **\[V\] Verified** — Claim confirmed by a primary authoritative source with direct link  
- **\[I\] Inferred** — Primary source supports the direction but not the exact figure  
- **\[H\] Hypothesis** — No primary source found; potential hallucination or unsupported claim

**AI Model used:** Claude (web search disabled) **Report generated:** April 2025 **Fact-check conducted by:** Jorge Baptista **Framework:** Decision Architect — V/I/H Epistemic Tagging

